Object.Field: Copy of LKM SQL to HBase SQOOP Direct
SNP_TRT : LKM SQL to Hive SQOOP

COMPONENT NAME: LKM SQL to HBase SQOOP Direct COMPONENT VERSION: 1 AUTHOR: Oracle COMPATIBILITY: ODI 12.1.3.0.1 and above DESCRIPTION: This KM extacts data from a JDBC data source and imports the data into HBase. It executes the following steps: 1. Create a SQOOP configuration file, which contains the upstream query. 2. Execute SQOOP to extract the source data and import into HBase This is a direct load LKM and must be used without any IKM. Additional information can be found in the KM option descriptions as well as in the Oracle BigDataConnector User's Guide.
Check this option, if you wish to create the target table. Default: false
Set this option to true, if you wish to replace any existing target table content with the new data.
